Applying RED in all relevant product families Our aim has been to intensify the use of lifecycle assess-

ments (LCAs) and environmental product declarations (EPDs), which will allow us to identify environmentally compatible design alternatives that take circularity into account and can be integrated into product specifications. Our ambition is to apply the RED approach to all relevant4

4 Relevant: All products, systems, solutions, and services whose sales are not negligible, that will not be discontinued in the foreseeable future, or are not part of a confirmed spin-off.